{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/GrowingDevlog/20240604_codeBlock_title/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"32's Dev.log","author":"han32","siteUrl":"https://gatsby-starter-bee.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"HSangMi/devlog"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"han32"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"62cf6b56-4800-548c-8310-b6c59f10bd3c","excerpt":"코드블록 타이틀 추가하기 1. 플러그인 설치 플러그인을 설치하게되면 에 추가됨 2. gatsby-config에 추가  플러그인 옵션 중 맨 위에 위치해야한다는 옵션이 있음 CSS 설정 저는 별도 className을 지정하지 않고 기본 class() 이름으로 지정 했습니다 3. 타이틀 설정하는 방법  추가 적용 완료! 2. 코드블록 라인넘버 표시하기","html":"<aside>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan\">@Jbee</a> 님의 블로그 템플릿을 받아서 사용 중 인데, 코드블록 디자인에 몇가지 설정을 추가하고 싶었다.  <br/>\n1. 테마 <br/>\n<b>2. 타이틀</b> <br/>\n2. 라인넘버 <br/>\n3. 하이라이트  <br/>\n</aside>\n<h2 id=\"코드블록-타이틀-추가하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%B8%94%EB%A1%9D-%ED%83%80%EC%9D%B4%ED%8B%80-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"코드블록 타이틀 추가하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>코드블록 타이틀 추가하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-플러그인-설치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-%ED%94%8C%EB%9F%AC%EA%B7%B8%EC%9D%B8-%EC%84%A4%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"1 플러그인 설치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. 플러그인 설치</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-bash line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> i gatsby-remark-code-titles</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>플러그인을 설치하게되면 <code class=\"language-text\">package.json</code>에 추가됨</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-code-title\">package.json</div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-json line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\ndependencies <span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"gatsby-remark-code-titles\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^1.1.0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-gatsby-config에-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-gatsby-config%EC%97%90-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"2 gatsby config에 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-